-- Zynix Premium Cheat
-- Original base: NoMercy v1 by Zywtx
-- Completely overhauled and upgraded to premium quality

-- CHANGELOG:
-- [Zynix v1.0.0]
-- + Complete rebranding to Zynix (UI, prints, naming)
-- + Modern premium UI with smooth animations, gradients, and hover effects
-- + Completely reworked ESP: accurate bounding box calculation with automatic sizing
-- + Skeleton ESP now fully supports R15 characters with all limb segments
-- + New Hitbox Expander with smooth size transitions (lerp) and visual overlay
--   - Blue outer circle shows expanded hitbox area
--   - White inner circle marks original hitbox size
-- + Aimbot now includes optional velocity prediction with configurable amount
-- + Triggerbot delay and anti-spam protection
-- + Fly mode now uses BodyVelocity for smooth, stable flight
-- + Spinbot, Bhop, NoClip, Fullbright refined for stability
-- + Added cleanup routines and error handling
-- + Performance optimizations and memory management
-- + Detailed code comments throughout
-- ==================================================

